The series formula_49 is the geometric series with common ratio formula_50, hence formula_51 which is finite. The sum formula_52 is a finite sum and hence it is bounded, this implies the series formula_53 converges by the monotone convergence theorem and the series formula_42 converges by the absolute convergence test.&lt;br&gt;
