* Dynamic Albedo of Neutrons (MSL)
* Hazcam (MER + MSL + M20)
* MarsDial (MER + MSL + M20)
* Materials Adherence Experiment (MPF)
* MIMOS II (MER)
* Mini-TES (MER)
* Mars Hand Lens Imager (MSL)
* Navcam (MER + MSL + M20+TW1)
* Pancam (MER)
* Rock Abrasion Tool (MER)
