** Mass in C major, Op. 86
* Franz Schubert
** &quot;Wanderer Fantasy&quot;, Op. 15 D. 760
** Fantasy for violin and piano, D. 934
** Sonata for 4-hands, D. 812 (&quot;Grand Duo&quot;)
